      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation must be verified under a documented QA process consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v19.2 was used under a documented software QA plan including version control, regression testing, and release validation. All QA records are archived and traceable."
    },
    {
