      "acceptanceCriteria": "Numerical code must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through benchmark test cases at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver was verified against standard benchmark cases including lid-driven cavity flow and pipe flow, confirming correct implementation of the Navier-Stokes equations and the power-law hemolysis model."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
