      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mesh refinement study must demonstrate discretization error below 5% for hemolysis index predictions at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted with mesh sizes of 1.2M, 3.8M, and 9.6M cells. Richardson extrapolation yielded a discretization error of 2.3% for the hemolysis index, meeting the acceptance criterion."
