    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors achieved their required levels at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrated discretization error below 5%, output agreement within 11% of experimental measurements, and relative hemolysis index RH below 1.0 for all worst-case operating conditions. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
